    <h3>Diversity in Canada</h3>
    <p>
        This dashboard is designed with the target audience in
        mind: Canadian or international visitors seeking a community or region
        that aligns with their cultural background or preferences. The
        dashboard offers a range of visualizations, including ethnic distribution
